 Paradice Investment Management Pty Ltd  




















Telephone: +61 2 8227 7400




Paradice Investment Management




















AWARDED FOR ALL THE RIGHT REASONS
Since its beginning in 2000, Paradice Investment Management has developed a solid track record of producing outstanding returns across its products.
Our aim has always been to add value for our investors and, since inception, all our funds have exceeded their benchmarks. We believe that excessive funds under management can hinder performance, so we closely monitor and constrain capacity as funds grow to their optimal size.







Kevin Beck Featured on Informed Investor
Paradice Global Small Mid Cap Fund Manager Kevin Beck was featured on the Informed Investor website, in this video Kevin provides some insight into his background as well as expanding on the Global Small Cap investment universe and what benefits investors to gain through allocating to the asset class. Please click here to view the video. CPD points can be attained by completing a short quiz at the end of the video. 



